cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.DS 

The paper deals with image processing and OCR, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of neural networks for artifact segmentation and recognition accuracy improvement suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the use of real-world datasets and the focus on performance improvement suggests a possible connection to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
